Neck Deep s highly anticipated sophomore full-length Life s Not Out To Get You is ready to be unleashed onto the world. The UK pop-punk quintet, along with the help of producers Jeremy McKinnon of A Day To Remember and Andrew Wade (The Ghost Inside, Issues), were able to create an album filled with amazing hooks that is sure to get fans singing along to their latest anthems
